WEBVTT

00:02.572 --> 00:04.408
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON "WEEDS"...</i>

00:04.442 --> 00:07.749
Silas: I JUST MOSTLY
HANG OUT, GET HIGH.

00:07.782 --> 00:09.285
YOU'RE AN IDIOT.
FUCK YOU.

00:09.318 --> 00:11.155
THAT WAS DAD'S LIGHTER.
HE GAVE IT TO ME!

00:11.189 --> 00:12.993
WHAT IS WRONG WITH YOU?!

00:13.026 --> 00:14.428
GIVE ME
YOUR FUCKING BAG.

00:14.462 --> 00:17.636
I JUST GOT RIPPED OFF BY SOME
CAMPUS COP AT VALLEY STATE.

00:17.669 --> 00:19.806
YOU'RE GONNA NEED MY PROTECTION
A LOT MORE THAN YOU THINK.

00:19.840 --> 00:21.242
YOUR RENT‐A‐COP
IS A DEALER HIMSELF.

00:21.276 --> 00:23.280
NICE HAIRCUT.
IT'S A WIG.

00:23.313 --> 00:25.885
OHHH, RIGHT,
THE CANCER THING.

00:25.919 --> 00:27.087
CAN I PET IT?

00:27.121 --> 00:28.691
I LOVE YOU.
WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING?

00:28.724 --> 00:29.993
HOW CAN I MAKE IT UP
TO YOU?

00:30.027 --> 00:32.464
HERE, THIS IS YOURS.
I DIDN'T REALIZE WHO YOU WERE.

00:32.498 --> 00:36.439
I MEAN, I‐I KNEW WHO YOU WERE.
I JUST DIDN'T KNOW WHO YOU WERE.

00:36.472 --> 00:37.542
I'm so sorry.

00:49.766 --> 00:52.906
♪♪ LITTLE BOXES ON THE HILLSIDE ♪♪

00:52.939 --> 00:55.410
♪♪ LITTLE BOXES
MADE OF TICKY‐TACKY ♪♪

00:55.444 --> 00:58.250
♪♪ LITTLE BOXES ON THE HILLSIDE ♪♪

00:58.283 --> 01:00.254
♪♪ LITTLE BOXES ALL THE SAME ♪♪

01:00.287 --> 01:03.193
♪♪ THERE'S A GREEN ONE
AND A PINK ONE ♪♪

01:03.226 --> 01:05.665
♪♪ AND A BLUE ONE
AND A YELLOW ONE ♪♪

01:05.698 --> 01:08.403
♪♪ AND THEY'RE ALL MADE OUT
OF TICKY‐TACKY ♪♪

01:08.436 --> 01:12.211
♪♪ AND THEY ALL LOOK
JUST THE SAME ♪♪

01:12.244 --> 01:15.083
♪♪ AND THE PEOPLE IN THE HOUSES ♪♪

01:15.117 --> 01:17.421
♪♪ ALL WENT TO THE UNIVERSITY ♪♪

01:17.454 --> 01:20.294
♪♪ WHERE THEY WERE PUT IN BOXES ♪♪

01:20.327 --> 01:23.099
♪♪ AND THEY CAME OUT
ALL THE SAME ♪♪

01:23.133 --> 01:25.772
♪♪ AND THERE'S DOCTORS
AND LAWYERS ♪♪

01:25.805 --> 01:28.577
♪♪ AND BUSINESS EXECUTIVES ♪♪

01:28.611 --> 01:31.015
♪♪ AND THEY'RE ALL MADE OUT
OF TICKY‐TACKY ♪♪

01:31.049 --> 01:35.290
♪♪ AND THEY ALL LOOK
JUST THE SAME ♪♪

01:36.794 --> 01:39.933
FEEL LIKE A BIG MAN?
HMM?

01:39.967 --> 01:42.137
ALL MACHO AND SHIT.

01:42.171 --> 01:43.841
SHE GOT JACKED
FOR LIKE 14 GRAND.

01:43.874 --> 01:46.547
SHE GOT JACKED
FOR 14 GRAND.

01:46.580 --> 01:47.882
NOT US.
NOT ME.

01:47.916 --> 01:51.022
NO, SEE, I GOT MY SHIT
TUCKED AWAY SAFE.

01:51.055 --> 01:54.028
BOY, IT WASN'T YOUR JOB
TO DEFEND HER.

01:54.061 --> 01:56.700
THAT MAN WAS JUST PROTECTING
WHAT WAS HIS,

01:56.734 --> 01:57.936
JUST LIKE ANY MAN WOULD.

01:57.969 --> 01:59.806
NO, BUT, SEE, YOU GOT
TO GO UP IN THERE

01:59.840 --> 02:02.779
AND BEAT THE SHIT OUT OF HIM
WITH YOUR LITTLE BUDDIES.

02:02.812 --> 02:04.683
FOR WHAT ‐‐ FOR HER?

02:04.716 --> 02:08.323
SO SHE THINK YOU A BIG MAN,
BIG STRONG MAN?

02:08.356 --> 02:10.628
YOU HER FUCKING ERRAND BOY.

02:10.662 --> 02:12.231
WELL, FUCK MY SHIT UP.

02:12.264 --> 02:14.368
AFTER ALL THE YEARS
I DONE SACRIFICED FOR YOU,

02:14.402 --> 02:16.205
FOR VANEETA, FOR EVERYBODY,
FOR WHAT ‐‐

02:16.239 --> 02:17.742
FOR SOMEBODY
WHO AIN'T EVEN FAMILY,

02:17.776 --> 02:21.082
SOMEBODY WHO DON'T KNOW
WHAT THE HELL SHE DOING?

02:21.115 --> 02:22.384
GROWING TOO BIG TOO FAST.

02:22.418 --> 02:23.521
SHE GONNA JUMP IN THERE

02:23.554 --> 02:25.591
BEFORE SHE EVEN KNOW
THE LAY OF THE LAND.

02:25.625 --> 02:28.296
YEAH, BUT, SEE, THERE YOU ARE
WITH A BIG OLD NET

02:28.330 --> 02:30.400
WAITING TO CATCH HER
JUST IN CASE SHE FALLS.

02:30.434 --> 02:32.137
SHE GONNA FALL,
ALL RIGHT.

02:32.171 --> 02:34.342
SHE GONNA FALL
AND LAND HER LILY‐WHITE ASS

02:34.375 --> 02:35.878
RIGHT ON TOP
OF YOUR HEAD.

02:35.912 --> 02:37.949
OH, HELL,
ON TOP OF MY HEAD.

02:37.982 --> 02:41.890
GRIND ALL OUR SHIT UP
INTO THE GROUND.

02:41.924 --> 02:43.561
I'M SORRY.
YES, YOU ARE.

02:43.594 --> 02:45.263
AND YOU AIN'T GONNA SEE
HER NO MORE.

02:45.297 --> 02:47.334
SHE COME OVER HERE,
YOU DISAPPEAR.

02:47.368 --> 02:50.474
YOU WILL HAVE NO CONTACT
WITH HER WHATSOEVER.

02:50.508 --> 02:53.213
I MEAN, YOU EVEN SEE
A WHITE GIRL ON TELEVISION,

02:53.246 --> 02:55.217
YOU CHANGE THE CHANNEL
OR I SWEAR FOR GOD,

02:55.250 --> 02:56.620
I WILL FREEZE YOU OUT
SO COLD,

02:56.653 --> 02:59.593
YOU'LL HAVE TO CARRY YOUR ASS
TO THE NORTH POLE TO DEFROST.

02:59.626 --> 03:01.563
YOU HEAR ME?

03:01.597 --> 03:03.466
I HEAR YOU.

03:08.978 --> 03:12.952
[ Weakly ] HEYLIA?
I'M WARNING YOU, LITTLE GIRL,
I AM IN NO MOOD.

03:12.986 --> 03:14.321
WHAT YOU WANT?

03:14.355 --> 03:15.390
I THINK I'M IN LABOR.

03:15.424 --> 03:18.697
MY GRANDBABY?
MY GRANDBABY'S COMING!

03:18.731 --> 03:21.837
OOH, LORD, LET'S GO.
COME ON, LET'S GO.

03:21.870 --> 03:23.641
GET MY BAG!

03:23.674 --> 03:25.277
Nancy: AND?

03:25.310 --> 03:28.083
NO BITING.
I'M SORRY.
I DIDN'T HEAR YOU.

03:28.116 --> 03:29.653
I'M NOT
GONNA BITE ANYONE!

03:29.686 --> 03:31.623
UNDER ANY CIRCUMSTANCES,
NO MATTER HOW PROVOKED

03:31.657 --> 03:33.594
OR UPSET YOU MIGHT BE,
THERE WILL BE NO BITING.

03:33.627 --> 03:36.567
STOP IT!
I'M NOT GONNA BITE!

03:36.600 --> 03:37.468
THANK YOU.

03:37.502 --> 03:41.075
LISTEN TO ME.
THANK YOU FOR NOT BITING.

03:41.109 --> 03:44.616
YOU'RE WELCOME.

03:44.649 --> 03:45.752
SMARTASS.

03:45.785 --> 03:49.425
YOU DON'T EVEN KNOW
IF HE'S GONNA BE THERE.

03:49.458 --> 03:51.830
WHO?
THAT GUY YOU LIKE ‐‐
PETER.

03:51.864 --> 03:54.101
I DON'T EVEN KNOW
IF I LIKE HIM.
HE'S CREEPY.

03:54.135 --> 03:57.609
HE'S NOT CREEPY.
YES, HE IS, AND HE SMELLS
LIKE FLEA COLLAR.

04:00.213 --> 04:02.852
WE HAVE TO GO.
WE'RE GONNA BE LATE.
OKAY.

04:04.088 --> 04:05.157
[ LAUGHS ]

04:05.190 --> 04:07.562
AND BOW. NICE JOB.

04:07.595 --> 04:09.533
GOOD CLEAN FIGHT ‐‐
CLEAN.

04:09.566 --> 04:10.535
NO TEETH.

04:10.568 --> 04:12.939
NO TEETH.
GO GET 'EM.

04:12.972 --> 04:14.910
[ SIGHS ]

04:17.114 --> 04:18.617
HEY.

04:18.651 --> 04:20.220
OH, HI...PETER.

04:20.253 --> 04:21.389
HI, PETER.

04:21.422 --> 04:24.128
NICE TO SEE YOU AGAIN.

04:24.161 --> 04:25.430
YOU TOO.

04:25.464 --> 04:28.203
I WAS HOPING
TO HEAR FROM YOU.
YEAH.

04:28.236 --> 04:30.440
I'VE BEEN MEANING
TO CALL.

04:30.474 --> 04:32.444
I SHOULD HAVE CALLED.

04:32.478 --> 04:35.618
DO YOU STILL HAVE
MY NUMBER?
I DO.
I HAVE IT.

04:35.651 --> 04:38.089
I'LL CALL YOU.

04:38.123 --> 04:39.960
WE'LL HAVE FUN.

04:39.993 --> 04:41.897
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

04:43.934 --> 04:45.838
[ SNARLING ]

04:48.777 --> 04:50.413
[ BARKING ]

04:54.388 --> 04:58.564
I GUESS SHANE'S REPUTATION
PRECEDES HIM.

04:58.597 --> 04:59.599
[ GROWLS ]

04:59.633 --> 05:02.939
OKAY, I'M THE CELEBRITY,
AND YOU BE THE PUBLICIST.

05:02.972 --> 05:04.375
YOU'RE SO HOT.

05:04.408 --> 05:07.749
REALLY?
YEAH, YOU'RE SO HOT.

05:07.782 --> 05:09.719
DO I LOOK HOT LIKE THIS?

05:09.753 --> 05:12.592
YEAH, YOU LOOK REALLY HOT
LIKE THAT.

05:15.497 --> 05:17.769
MOM, UM,
CAN PEGGY SLEEP OVER?

05:17.802 --> 05:21.309
WELL, SHE DOESN'T HAVE ANY
OF HER OVERNIGHT THINGS ‐‐

05:21.342 --> 05:22.779
WE HAVE
EXTRA TOOTHBRUSHES,

05:22.812 --> 05:25.852
AND TOMORROW SHE CAN BORROW
ONE OF MY INCENTIVE OUTFITS.

05:25.885 --> 05:27.287
ALL THE TAGS ARE STILL ON.

05:27.321 --> 05:28.657
YOU'RE SO HOT.

05:33.199 --> 05:35.170
YOU HAVE EXCELLENT HAIR,
AND YOU KNOW IT.

05:35.203 --> 05:36.907
It's an $8 haircut.

05:36.940 --> 05:38.343
IT SMELLS GOOD.

05:38.376 --> 05:40.480
WHEN DID YOU
SMELL MY HAIR?
At the restaurant.

05:40.515 --> 05:43.486
THERE WERE OVERTONES OF TOMATO
SAUCE AND GARLIC BREAD,

05:43.521 --> 05:46.425
but underneath,
it smelled clean and leafy.

05:46.459 --> 05:47.929
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

05:47.962 --> 05:50.333
OH, SHIT, THAT'S MY DOORBELL.
WHAT TIME IS IT?

05:50.367 --> 05:52.437
A QUARTER AFTER 1:00.

05:52.471 --> 05:54.543
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

05:54.576 --> 05:57.114
OH, GOD, I GOT TO GO.

05:57.147 --> 05:58.349
WE'RE ON FOR TOMORROW?
Yeah.

05:58.383 --> 05:59.418
YEAH, BYE.

05:59.451 --> 06:00.888
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

06:06.800 --> 06:07.769
MOMMY.

06:07.802 --> 06:09.338
IS THIS YOUR SON?

06:09.371 --> 06:11.275
[ Chuckling ]
HI, MOMMY.

06:11.309 --> 06:12.645
WHAT DID YOU DO?

06:12.679 --> 06:13.981
WE CAUGHT
HIM AND HIS GIRLFRIEND

06:14.014 --> 06:16.152
BREAKING INTO ONE OF THE MODEL
HOMES, HIGH ON SOMETHING.

06:16.185 --> 06:17.487
WE'RE GUESSING ECSTASY.

06:17.522 --> 06:19.458
YOU TOLD ME
YOU WERE SLEEPING AT BRIAN'S.

06:19.491 --> 06:22.431
OH, I AM SO THIRSTY.
DO WE HAVE GRAPE SODA?

06:22.464 --> 06:23.601
IT HAS TO BE GRAPE.

06:23.634 --> 06:25.470
WHOA, WHOA.
UH, OFFICER,

06:25.504 --> 06:31.182
I WILL ATTEND TO THIS IN A ‐‐
A GRAVE AND SERIOUS FASHION.

06:31.215 --> 06:32.785
YOU KNOW, UM,
TAKING ECSTASY'S

06:32.819 --> 06:35.323
LIKE TAKING ICE CREAM SCOOPS
OUT OF THE BRAIN.

06:35.357 --> 06:36.994
YEAH.

06:37.027 --> 06:39.031
WH‐WHERE IS MEGAN?

06:39.064 --> 06:42.237
OH, SHE'S OUT IN THE CAR WITH
MY PARTNER BEING VERY DIFFICULT,

06:42.271 --> 06:43.707
WON'T RESPOND
TO ANY QUESTIONS.

06:43.741 --> 06:46.813
OH. [ CHUCKLES ]
UM, SHE ‐‐ SHE'S DEAF.

06:46.847 --> 06:48.249
SERIOUSLY?

06:48.283 --> 06:51.255
TOLD YOU!
SILAS!

06:51.289 --> 06:52.424
DO YOU NEED HER ADDRESS?

06:52.457 --> 06:56.399
YES, MA'AM, PLEASE.
THANK YOU.

06:56.432 --> 06:59.104
I WANT TO THANK YOU
SO MUCH FOR, UM...

06:59.138 --> 07:01.008
BRINGING MY SON HOME,
OFFICER,

07:01.042 --> 07:04.549
AND I PROMISE THAT THIS WILL
NEVER, EVER...HAPPEN AGAIN.

07:04.582 --> 07:06.753
THIS IS A VERY CRITICAL TIME
IN YOUR CHILD'S LIFE.

07:06.787 --> 07:09.826
HIS ‐‐ HIS BRAIN
IS DEVELOPING.

07:09.859 --> 07:14.669
YOU DON'T WANT IT ALL HOLLOWED
OUT BY THE TIME HE'S 20.

07:14.703 --> 07:17.407
I CERTAINLY DON'T,
OFFICER.

07:17.441 --> 07:20.013
UH, GOOD NIGHT.
ICE CREAM SCOOPS.

07:23.453 --> 07:25.023
MOM, THIS IS ‐‐

07:25.056 --> 07:29.799
THIS IS THE SOFTEST THING I HAVE
EVER FELT IN MY ENTIRE LIFE.

07:29.833 --> 07:34.041
WELL, ENJOY IT BECAUSE
WHEN YOU COME DOWN,

07:34.074 --> 07:39.986
I AM GOING TO MAKE YOUR LIFE
UNBELIEVABLY HARD.

07:40.020 --> 07:41.022
[ LAUGHS ]

07:41.055 --> 07:42.892
[ CHUCKLES MOCKINGLY ]

08:02.230 --> 08:03.199
IS THAT FOR YOU?

08:03.232 --> 08:05.170
YEAH.

08:05.203 --> 08:07.407
SEE?
"ANDREW BOTWIN."

08:07.441 --> 08:08.610
THAT'S A LETTER FOR ME

08:08.644 --> 08:10.981
'CAUSE I'M SOMEONE
WHO GETS MAIL.

08:11.015 --> 08:12.150
[ PAPER RUSTLES ]

08:16.359 --> 08:18.129
WHAT?

08:23.039 --> 08:26.112
THEY WANT TO SEND ME
TO IRAQ, LUPITA.

08:26.145 --> 08:28.517
BYE.

08:31.723 --> 08:33.794
Girl: YOU'RE SO HOT.

08:44.348 --> 08:46.653
OH, GOOD CHRIST.

08:51.395 --> 08:52.965
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

08:56.439 --> 08:58.209
[ Sighing ]
THEY FOUND ME, MAN.

08:58.242 --> 09:00.280
BUMMER.

09:00.313 --> 09:02.184
WHO FOUND YOU?

09:02.217 --> 09:05.891
THE FUCKING ARMY,
THAT'S WHO.

09:05.925 --> 09:10.701
YEARS AGO IN COLORADO,
I WAS TRYING TO...

09:11.770 --> 09:14.743
IMPRESS A LADY FRIEND,
AND THERE WAS JAGERMEISTER,

09:14.776 --> 09:17.314
AND I SIGNED UP
FOR THE ARMY RESERVES.

09:17.347 --> 09:18.550
THEN I FORGOT ABOUT IT.

09:18.584 --> 09:21.523
NOW I GET A LETTER SAYING
I GOT TO REPORT FOR DUTY

09:21.556 --> 09:23.392
OR FACE MILITARY PRISON.

09:23.426 --> 09:25.497
I DON'T ‐‐
HOW DID THEY FIND ME?

09:25.531 --> 09:28.704
I MEAN, I'M OFF THE GRID.
I'M OFF‐THE‐GRID ANDY.

09:28.737 --> 09:30.975
WELL, YOU GOT BUSTED
FOR POSSESSION,

09:31.008 --> 09:33.246
AND NOW YOU'RE
"IN‐THE‐SYSTEM ANDY."

09:33.279 --> 09:36.218
YOU GOT TO HELP ME, MAN.
YOU'RE ON THE CITY COUNCIL.

09:36.252 --> 09:38.089
TELL THEM
THAT MY CITY NEEDS ME.

09:38.122 --> 09:39.425
NEEDS YOU FOR WHAT?

09:39.458 --> 09:42.097
I DON'T KNOW.
FOR ‐‐ FOR PLANTING TREES...

09:42.130 --> 09:45.336
STARTING A YOUTH PROGRAM
FOR TROUBLED TEENAGE GIRLS.

09:45.370 --> 09:48.209
I CAN HELP YOU IF YOU GET A
TICKET FOR LITTERING IN A PARK,

09:48.242 --> 09:49.445
BUT THAT'S ALL THE JUICE
I GOT.

09:49.478 --> 09:52.050
FINE ‐‐ THEN I'M
A CONSCIENTIOUS OBJECTOR.

09:52.083 --> 09:55.457
YOU SIGNED FOR THE RESERVES
ON YOUR OWN DRUNK, HORNY ACCORD.

09:55.490 --> 09:57.160
[ Chuckling ]
YOU ARE FUCKED.

09:57.194 --> 09:59.331
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

09:59.364 --> 10:00.701
[ SIGHS ]

10:00.734 --> 10:03.239
OH, WELL, I AM NOT GOING
TO IRAQ

10:03.272 --> 10:07.347
TO FIGHT IN SOME BULLSHIT WAR
ABOUT OIL MONEY.

10:07.380 --> 10:08.584
BULLSHIT WAR?

10:08.617 --> 10:11.723
WHAT ABOUT 9/11?
DIDN'T IRAN HIDE THE TERRORISTS?

10:13.426 --> 10:15.096
WE'RE FIGHTING
A WAR IN IRAQ, DOUG,

10:15.130 --> 10:16.900
AND NEITHER COUNTRY
HAD ANYTHING TO DO

10:16.933 --> 10:18.770
WITH BLOWING UP
THE WORLD TRADE CENTER.

10:18.804 --> 10:21.175
WELL, THEY BOTH HAVE SAND.

10:21.208 --> 10:24.481
BUSH INVADED A SOVEREIGN NATION
IN DEFIANCE OF THE U. N.

10:24.516 --> 10:25.784
HE'S A WAR CRIMINAL,

10:25.818 --> 10:28.724
AND NOW I'M SUPPOSED TO BE
ONE OF HIS DISPOSABLE THUGS

10:28.757 --> 10:32.130
WITH A FUCKING TARGET ON MY HEAD
IN THE MIDDLE OF THE DESERT,

10:32.164 --> 10:35.436
WAITING TO BE BLOWN UP BY A CAR
BOMB RIGGED BY A 12‐YEAR‐OLD

10:35.470 --> 10:37.274
WHO LOVED "FRIENDS"
AND METALLICA

10:37.307 --> 10:40.280
UNTIL ONE OF OUR MISSILES
BLEW UP HIS HOUSE?!

10:40.313 --> 10:41.750
I DON'T THINK SO.

10:41.783 --> 10:44.454
THEY HAD WEAPONS
OF MASS DESTRUCTION.

10:44.488 --> 10:47.127
THERE WERE NO WEAPONS
OF MASS DESTRUCTION!

10:47.160 --> 10:49.498
NO?

10:49.532 --> 10:50.901
WELL, WHATEVER.

10:50.935 --> 10:52.304
LOOK, I GOT
A LOT OF SHIT TO DO.

10:52.337 --> 10:55.109
YOU NAME ME ONE THING YOU HAVE
TO DO THAT'S MORE IMPORTANT

10:55.143 --> 10:57.380
THAN THE CORPORATE TAKEOVER
OF OUR DEMOCRACY.

10:57.414 --> 10:59.652
I GOT TO TAKE A SHIT.

11:01.355 --> 11:02.525
YOU GOT TO HELP ME, MAN.

11:02.558 --> 11:04.194
I WILL, I WILL.

11:04.228 --> 11:07.434
I'M GONNA PUT ONE OF THOSE
YELLOW‐RIBBON STICKERS

11:07.467 --> 11:09.739
ON MY CAR...FOR YOU.

11:13.514 --> 11:16.118
HOW CAN YOU BE
SO BLINDLY PRO BUSH?

11:16.151 --> 11:19.157
I LIKE HIS WIFE, LAURA.

11:19.191 --> 11:22.163
USED TO BUY WEED
FROM HER AT S. M. U.

11:22.197 --> 11:24.001
GOOD SHIT.

11:24.034 --> 11:25.971
GOOD SHIT.

11:28.744 --> 11:30.380
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

11:30.413 --> 11:32.017
SILAS?

11:48.784 --> 11:51.155
WHAT HAPPENED
AT THE HOSPITAL?

11:51.188 --> 11:54.228
SENT HER HOME.
CAN'T EVEN HAVE A BABY RIGHT.

11:54.261 --> 11:58.670
I WANT TO SHOW YOU SOMETHING
I'VE BEEN WORKING ON.

11:58.704 --> 12:00.874
A SUPER STRAIN.
GROW ANYTIME, ANYWHERE.

12:00.908 --> 12:02.310
NOT IN WEST ADAMS,
IT WON'T.

12:02.344 --> 12:05.216
YOU GONNA BE A DEALER OR
A FUCKING GARDENER, PEDRO?

12:05.250 --> 12:08.690
HEYLIA, IN ORDER FOR US
TO GROW, WE HAVE TO GROW.

12:08.724 --> 12:10.126
WE DON'T NEED NO LAND.

12:10.159 --> 12:11.863
IT'S HYRDO.
ALL WE NEED IS WAREHOUSE SPACE.

12:11.896 --> 12:14.201
LET IT GO, CONRAD.
LET IT GO?

12:14.234 --> 12:16.171
I DON'T WANT TO BE A MIDDLEMAN
FOR THE REST OF MY LIFE.

12:16.205 --> 12:20.179
NEGRO, PLEASE, YOU STILL GOT TO
WORK YOUR WAY UP TO THE MIDDLE.

12:20.213 --> 12:23.252
OUR GROWERS ARE STARTING TO SELL
EXCLUSIVELY TO THE CLUBS,

12:23.286 --> 12:25.557
WHICH MEANS THAT WE GOT
TO GET INTO THIS NOW.

12:25.591 --> 12:27.127
I'M TELLING YOU IF ‐‐
ENOUGH!

12:27.160 --> 12:30.500
NOW, THIS MY BUSINESS.
YOU WORK FOR ME.

12:30.534 --> 12:32.370
OH, SHIT!

12:32.404 --> 12:34.374
IS SHE IN LABOR?

12:34.408 --> 12:36.178
ALREADY BEEN
TO THE HOSPITAL.

12:36.211 --> 12:38.215
AIN'T BUT TWO CENTIMETERS
DILATED.

12:38.249 --> 12:40.119
THIS ONE GONNA BE A WHILE.
FUCK YOU!

12:40.153 --> 12:41.923
THAT'S RIGHT, BABY.
LET IT ALL OUT.

12:41.957 --> 12:43.794
GO TO YOUR HAPPY PLACE.

12:43.827 --> 12:46.766
SO, CONRAD,
NICE PLANT.

12:46.800 --> 12:49.371
YOU WORKING ON
A NEW SPECIAL BLEND FOR ME?

12:51.543 --> 12:52.812
WHAT'S THE MATTER?

12:52.845 --> 12:54.481
OH, HE'S NOT HERE.

12:54.515 --> 12:56.686
OH, REALLY?
[ CHUCKLES ]

12:56.720 --> 12:59.391
HE COMING BACK SOON?

12:59.424 --> 13:01.428
NO. HE'S NOT.

13:01.462 --> 13:02.865
NOT WHILE YOU HERE.

13:02.898 --> 13:04.736
WHAT'S THAT SUPPOSED
TO MEAN?

13:04.769 --> 13:06.305
THAT MEANS
THAT FROM NOW ON,

13:06.338 --> 13:08.777
IF YOU GOT BUSINESS TO HANDLE,
YOU HANDLE IT WITH ME.

13:08.810 --> 13:11.215
YOU AND CONRAD AIN'T HAVING
NO MORE ASSOCIATION,

13:11.248 --> 13:14.522
NOT WHILE I'M ALIVE AND KICKING
WITH MY POINTY SHOES.

13:14.555 --> 13:15.824
I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

13:15.858 --> 13:18.496
WHAT DID I DO?
YOU BROUGHT OUT
THE STUPID IN HIM.

13:18.530 --> 13:20.166
NOW, I'M SURE
YOU DIDN'T TELL HIM

13:20.199 --> 13:22.203
TO GO DOWN
TO THAT LITTLE SCHOOL

13:22.237 --> 13:25.476
AND BEAT THE TAR OUT
OF LITTLE MR. SECURITY GUARD,

13:25.511 --> 13:27.280
BUT YOU BLINK
THEM BIG BROWN EYES,

13:27.314 --> 13:30.386
AND THERE HE GOES,
AND I CAN'T HAVE THAT.

13:30.420 --> 13:31.756
YOU DID THAT?

13:31.790 --> 13:34.796
WHO DO YOU THINK DONE IT,
THE FUCK‐YOU‐UP FAIRY?

13:34.829 --> 13:35.998
I DIDN'T ‐‐

13:36.031 --> 13:39.271
I HAD NO IDEA.
I NEVER WOULD HAVE ‐‐

13:39.304 --> 13:40.340
AND YOU NEVER WILL.

13:40.373 --> 13:43.112
SO, YOU WANT TO KEEP
ON DOING BUSINESS OVER HERE,

13:43.145 --> 13:45.818
YOU GONNA DO IT
WITH ME AND VANEETA.

13:45.851 --> 13:47.420
YOU CAN'T TELL ME
WHO TO TALK TO.

13:49.391 --> 13:52.097
CONRAD, SAY SOMETHING.

14:00.213 --> 14:01.816
HE'S MY FRIEND.

14:01.850 --> 14:04.354
WHAT'S IT GONNA BE?

14:04.388 --> 14:06.291
YOU GONNA PLAY...

14:06.325 --> 14:09.064
OR ARE YOU GET THE FUCK UP OUT
MY KITCHEN AND NEVER COME BACK?

14:09.097 --> 14:11.836
THAT'S N‐NOT
A FAIR CHOICE.

14:11.870 --> 14:15.009
FARE IS WHAT YOU PAY
TO RIDE THE BUS.

14:15.043 --> 14:18.082
SEE, THAT'S
THE ONLY FAIR I KNOW.

14:21.255 --> 14:22.658
FORGET IT.

14:22.691 --> 14:24.929
I'M OUT OF HERE.

14:24.962 --> 14:26.766
YOU SURE ABOUT THAT?

14:26.800 --> 14:27.835
MAYBE.

14:27.868 --> 14:29.037
MAYBE.

14:29.071 --> 14:31.843
YOU HEAR THAT SHIT, VANEETA?
SHE SAID "MAYBE."

14:31.876 --> 14:33.547
I THINK
MY WATER JUST BROKE.

14:33.580 --> 14:36.051
ON MY GOOD CHAIR?

14:36.085 --> 14:38.222
GIRL, YOU DIDN'T THINK TO PUT
A TOWEL DOWN BEFORE ‐‐

14:38.255 --> 14:39.324
MOMMY!

14:39.357 --> 14:42.497
ALL RIGHT, BABY, I'M COMING.
I'M COMING.

14:42.531 --> 14:45.136
THANK YOU.

14:45.169 --> 14:48.109
SO, HOW DO YOU KNOW NANCY?

14:51.181 --> 14:54.054
OUR, UH,
SONS DO KARATE TOGETHER.

14:54.087 --> 14:55.858
HAVE YOU...
KNOWN EACH OTHER LONG?

14:55.891 --> 14:58.129
NO, WE MET
A FEW WEEKS AGO.

14:58.162 --> 15:00.199
[ CLEARS THROAT ]
HEY, CAN I GET A MUFFIN?

15:00.233 --> 15:01.903
WHAT ARE YOUR INTENTIONS
WITH NANCY?

15:01.936 --> 15:05.911
I INTEND TO HAVE COFFEE
WITH HER...AND A MUFFIN.

15:05.944 --> 15:08.717
SHE'S A REMARKABLE WOMAN ‐‐

15:08.750 --> 15:11.856
STRONG YET FEMININE,

15:11.890 --> 15:16.298
BRAVE AND BOLD WITH...
BEAUTIFUL SKIN.

15:16.331 --> 15:18.503
YES.

15:18.537 --> 15:21.676
LOVELY...LOVELY SKIN.

15:21.709 --> 15:24.281
HOW'S THE BANANA NUT?

15:24.314 --> 15:25.751
DO YOU LOVE HER?

15:25.784 --> 15:27.822
PETER, I'M SO SORRY
I'M LATE.

15:27.855 --> 15:30.828
SO, YOU DO KNOW THIS GUY.

15:30.861 --> 15:33.299
YES, I DO, SANJAY.
THANK YOU.

15:33.332 --> 15:36.138
HE SAYS
HE WANTS A MUFFIN.

15:36.171 --> 15:38.175
THEN GET HIM...A MUFFIN.

15:38.209 --> 15:40.714
ARE YOU SURE THAT'S WHAT
YOU WANT ME TO DO?

15:40.747 --> 15:42.117
YES, I DO.

15:42.150 --> 15:44.488
WOULD YOU LEAVE US ALONE
FOR A SECOND?

15:44.522 --> 15:45.456
TOASTED, PLEASE.

15:45.490 --> 15:49.464
FINE, BUT I'LL BE CLOSE BY
IF YOU NEED ME.

15:49.498 --> 15:50.634
Okay.

15:53.472 --> 15:55.944
HE'S, UH...

15:55.978 --> 15:58.282
VERY PROTECTIVE OF YOU.
[ CHUCKLES ]

15:58.315 --> 15:59.585
PUPPY LOVE.

15:59.619 --> 16:00.821
SMART PUPPY.

16:00.854 --> 16:02.625
LISTEN, PETER...

16:02.658 --> 16:05.597
OOH, I HATE SENTENCES
THAT START WITH "LISTEN."

16:05.631 --> 16:07.968
THEY NEVER FINISH WITH "YOU'VE
JUST WON A MILLION DOLLARS,"

16:08.002 --> 16:10.473
OR "I NEED TO RIP
YOUR CLOTHES OFF WITHIN
THE NEXT FIVE MINUTES."

16:10.507 --> 16:12.545
I ACTUALLY HAVE TO LEAVE
IN THE NEXT FIVE MINUTES.

16:12.578 --> 16:15.216
I HAVE SOME THINGS I HAVE
TO DEAL WITH, AND SILAS AND ‐‐

16:15.249 --> 16:16.619
SEE?

16:16.653 --> 16:18.355
MAYBE OUR TIMING'S JUST...

16:18.389 --> 16:21.161
BAD.
MAYBE YOU'RE JUST HAVING
A BUSY DAY.

16:21.195 --> 16:24.234
SO, YOU CAN'T HAVE COFFEE
WITH ME RIGHT NOW.

16:24.267 --> 16:26.171
THAT'S OKAY.

16:26.205 --> 16:28.342
I'M GONNA BE ALONE
THIS WEEKEND.

16:28.375 --> 16:29.745
TIM'S STAYING
WITH HIS MOTHER.

16:29.779 --> 16:35.323
MY LIFE'S NOT GONNA GET ANY LESS
COMPLICATED ANYTIME SOON.

16:35.356 --> 16:36.793
[ SIGHS ]

16:36.826 --> 16:38.630
[ CHUCKLES ]

16:38.663 --> 16:40.499
I'M TRYING HERE, NANCY.
I'M REALLY TRYING.

16:40.534 --> 16:42.571
I KNOW YOU ARE,
AND I REALLY APPRECIATE IT.

16:42.605 --> 16:44.542
I JUST, UM ‐‐

16:46.679 --> 16:49.117
MAYBE ANOTHER TIME
IN MY LIFE.

16:49.150 --> 16:50.486
420 ROD McKUEN LANE.

16:53.058 --> 16:54.829
I'M NOT
PROMISING ANYTHING.

16:54.862 --> 16:56.298
I'M NOT ASKING YOU TO.

17:02.076 --> 17:03.613
MUFFIN...

17:04.849 --> 17:07.521
TO GO.
GREAT.

17:07.555 --> 17:09.124
Celia: OKAY...

17:09.157 --> 17:11.161
YOU CANNOT BECOME
A LESBIAN

17:11.194 --> 17:14.100
JUST BECAUSE YOU DON'T WANT
TO LOSE WEIGHT.

17:15.303 --> 17:18.543
THE ONLY GIRL THAT YOU SHOULD BE
SEEING IS JENNY CRAIG.

17:18.577 --> 17:20.146
WHAT?
I KNOW, I KNOW.

17:20.179 --> 17:22.383
YOU SEE PEOPLE LIKE
ROSIE O'DONNELL,

17:22.417 --> 17:25.056
AND YOU THINK,
"HEY, SHE CAN FIND LOVE,"

17:25.089 --> 17:29.599
BUT THAT IS NOT WHERE LESBIANISM
IS GOING, ISABEL.

17:29.632 --> 17:31.769
LOOK AT "THE 'L' WORD."

17:31.803 --> 17:34.107
I LOVE PEGGY,
AND SHE LOVES ME.

17:34.140 --> 17:36.411
SHE'S A LITTLE ASIAN GIRL.
THEY LOOK LIKE BOYS ALREADY.

17:36.445 --> 17:37.915
YOU MIGHT AS WELL
GO FOR THE REAL DEAL.

17:37.948 --> 17:40.419
HEY, I HAVE BOOBS.
THOSE ARE NOT BOOBS.

17:41.522 --> 17:42.758
CALL YOUR GRANDPARENTS

17:42.791 --> 17:46.198
AND TELL THEM TO COME
AND PICK YOU UP, PLEASE.

17:48.068 --> 17:49.137
I KNEW IT WOULDN'T LAST.

17:49.170 --> 17:51.375
WHAT?
THE NEW IMPROVED YOU.

17:51.408 --> 17:54.180
YOU'RE FEELING BETTER,
AREN'T YOU?

17:54.214 --> 17:55.751
YOU'RE NOT GONNA DIE.

17:55.784 --> 17:57.220
NO.

17:57.253 --> 18:00.326
I'M GOING TO LIVE
FOR A LONG, LONG TIME.

18:00.359 --> 18:04.301
THE DOCTORS SAY I'M DOING
REALLY, REALLY WELL.

18:04.334 --> 18:07.040
YOU KNOW, MAYBE YOU SHOULD
DOUBLE‐CHECK JUST TO BE SURE.

18:07.073 --> 18:09.612
I MEAN, THERE'S STILL
SOME CHANCE YOU'LL DIE, RIGHT?

18:09.645 --> 18:11.281
WHY WOULD YOU SAY THAT?

18:11.315 --> 18:13.352
'CAUSE WHEN YOU THINK
YOU'RE GONNA DIE,

18:13.385 --> 18:15.222
YOU'RE A MUCH BETTER PERSON.

18:17.661 --> 18:20.132
[ SPEAKING CHINESE ]

18:25.176 --> 18:27.146
THEY'RE ON THEIR WAY.

18:28.683 --> 18:30.486
HERE.

18:30.520 --> 18:32.558
CUT OFF MY TOE.

18:32.591 --> 18:33.693
WHAT?

18:33.727 --> 18:35.429
[ GROANS ]

18:41.241 --> 18:43.445
IS THIS FOR REAL?
YES, JUST DO IT.

18:47.554 --> 18:49.224
ARE YOU OUT OF YOUR MIND?!
THAT'S MY TOE!

18:49.257 --> 18:50.527
YOU ASKED ME.

18:50.560 --> 18:52.564
[ SIGHS ]

18:52.598 --> 18:53.800
OKAY.

18:53.833 --> 18:55.937
I'M NOT THINKING CLEARLY.
IT'S OBVIOUS WHAT I HAVE TO DO.

18:55.971 --> 18:59.144
I HAVE
TO MOVE TO VERMONT...

18:59.177 --> 19:01.448
AND GET A BOYFRIEND
AND MARRY HIM.

19:08.797 --> 19:10.567
LOOK WHO'S AWAKE.

19:15.242 --> 19:16.746
HOW ARE YOU FEELING?

19:16.779 --> 19:18.516
LIKE...CRAP.

19:18.550 --> 19:23.258
WELL, REMEMBER IT FONDLY 'CAUSE
IT'S ALL DOWNHILL FROM HERE.

19:23.292 --> 19:25.229
WE WERE
JUST SCREWING AROUND.

19:25.262 --> 19:26.666
YOU TOOK ECSTASY.

19:26.699 --> 19:30.072
THAT SHIT IS LIKE TAKING ICE
CREAM SCOOPS OUT OF YOUR BRAIN.

19:30.106 --> 19:31.475
HOW ORIGINAL.

19:31.509 --> 19:36.051
I MAY HAVE BEEN FUCKED UP, BUT
I HEARD OFFICER FRIENDLY, TOO.

19:36.084 --> 19:38.489
OH, YOU THINK
YOU'RE CUTE?

19:38.523 --> 19:41.228
I SWEAR TO GOD, SILAS, IF I HAVE
TO LOCK YOU IN YOUR ROOM

19:41.261 --> 19:42.330
UNTIL YOU GET SOME SENSE,
I WILL.

19:42.363 --> 19:44.200
YOU DON'T FUCK AROUND
WITH DRUGS.

19:44.234 --> 19:45.369
THIS...FROM YOU?

19:45.403 --> 19:49.210
YOU'RE THE BIGGEST HYPOCRITE
ON EARTH.

19:49.244 --> 19:51.181
I DON'T TAKE DRUGS.

19:51.214 --> 19:54.054
WHEN HAVE YOU EVER SEEN ME
TAKE DRUGS?

19:54.087 --> 19:56.191
YOU MAY NOT TAKE THEM,
BUT...

19:56.224 --> 19:57.427
[ ZIPPER ZIPS ]

19:59.297 --> 20:01.301
...YOU SURE DO SELL THEM.

20:06.044 --> 20:07.848
I LIVE HERE, TOO, MOM.

20:07.881 --> 20:09.585
OR HAVE YOU NOT NOTICED

20:09.618 --> 20:13.092
BECAUSE YOU'VE BEEN SO BUSY
WITH YOUR BUSINESS?

20:13.125 --> 20:15.362
I'M NOT AN IDIOT.

20:17.668 --> 20:19.605
LISTEN...

20:22.276 --> 20:24.380
I'M NOT A DRUG ADDICT.

20:24.414 --> 20:26.318
YEAH, I LIKE TO DO
A LITTLE WEED,

20:26.351 --> 20:28.355
AND I TRIED "E"
FOR THE FIRST TIME.

20:28.388 --> 20:30.426
ROLLING WAS FUN ‐‐
TOTALLY, TOTALLY FUN,

20:30.459 --> 20:32.765
BUT I'M NOT RUNNING OUT THE DOOR
TO SCORE MORE.

20:32.798 --> 20:34.434
LOOK, I DON'T BLAME YOU
FOR WHAT YOU DO.

20:34.467 --> 20:38.208
YOU'RE DOING WHAT YOU NEED
TO DO, I GUESS.

20:38.242 --> 20:41.481
LET'S JUST STAY
OUT OF EACH OTHER'S WAY.

20:41.516 --> 20:43.218
YOU'RE 16,
AND I'M YOUR MOTHER.

20:43.252 --> 20:45.289
NO.
NO?

20:45.322 --> 20:47.360
I'M NOT GIVING YOU
CARTE BLANCHE AT 16

20:47.393 --> 20:49.164
TO DO WHATEVER THE HELL
YOU WANT

20:49.197 --> 20:51.301
BECAUSE I MADE
A QUESTIONABLE DECISION.

20:51.334 --> 20:52.871
WHAT CHOICE DO YOU HAVE?

20:52.905 --> 20:55.209
I HAVE THE CHOICE TO KICK YOU
OUT OF THIS HOUSE.

20:55.242 --> 20:57.180
OH, YOU WANT TO EXPLAIN
THAT TO SHANE?

20:57.213 --> 20:59.685
NO, OF COURSE NOT.
HE'S BEEN THROUGH ENOUGH.

20:59.718 --> 21:01.188
WE ALL HAVE.

21:01.221 --> 21:04.360
LET'S JUST
BE PEACEFUL, OKAY?

21:04.394 --> 21:06.198
JUST DO OUR THING.

21:06.231 --> 21:08.570
I'M GOING TO MEGAN'S.

21:20.827 --> 21:22.531
[ GATE CLOSES ]

21:41.301 --> 21:42.604
WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING?

21:42.638 --> 21:44.474
PRACTICING TO BE DEAD
IN CASE I GO TO IRAQ.

21:44.508 --> 21:46.779
THERE'S VERY LITTLE WATER
IN IRAQ.

21:46.813 --> 21:49.284
THEN I'LL FLOAT IN A POOL
OF BLOOD...OR OIL.

21:49.317 --> 21:51.321
WHATEVER THEY GOT,
I'M READY TO FLOAT.

21:51.354 --> 21:53.325
I'M SINKING.
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

21:53.358 --> 21:56.298
SILAS JUST INFORMED ME
THAT I HAVE NO PARENTAL RIGHTS

21:56.331 --> 21:58.001
BECAUSE I'M A DRUG DEALER.

21:58.035 --> 21:59.638
HOW THE FUCK
DID HE FIND OUT?

21:59.672 --> 22:04.280
HOW THE FUCK DID YOU THINK
HE WOULDN'T, WEEDY McWEEDWEED?

22:04.314 --> 22:09.357
I DON'T HAVE TO APOLOGIZE
FOR BEING A WEED DEALER.

22:09.390 --> 22:11.529
IT'S A CHOICE I MADE.

22:11.562 --> 22:15.102
I HAPPEN TO BE
VERY GOOD AT IT,

22:15.135 --> 22:17.708
PROVIDING FOR MY FAMILY.

22:17.741 --> 22:19.678
AND I'M NOT SORRY.

22:19.712 --> 22:21.816
WELL, YOU DON'T
HAVE TO BE SORRY.

22:21.849 --> 22:24.254
HE'S NOT MAD AT YOU
FOR SELLING DRUGS.

22:24.287 --> 22:26.391
HE'S MAD AT YOU
FOR LYING TO HIM.

22:26.424 --> 22:29.063
SO, HE HIT HIS BROTHER,
AND HE TOOK ECSTASY?

22:29.097 --> 22:31.001
ECSTASY'S A WHOLE LOT
OF FUN.

22:31.034 --> 22:34.875
I DON'T WANT TO CHOOSE BETWEEN
MY BUSINESS AND MY FAMILY.

22:34.909 --> 22:38.181
YOU DON'T HAVE TO.

22:38.215 --> 22:42.056
YOU GOT TO BE HONEST WITH YOUR
FAMILY ABOUT YOUR BUSINESS.

22:42.089 --> 22:43.458
TELL SHANE?

22:45.162 --> 22:47.734
UNLESS YOU WANT
A REPEAT PERFORMANCE.

22:53.278 --> 22:54.815
YO.

22:57.453 --> 22:59.892
SO YOU'RE TALKING
TO ME NOW.

23:06.672 --> 23:09.545
WHAT'S THAT ‐‐
A GOING‐AWAY PRESENT?

23:09.578 --> 23:11.649
I DON'T WANT IT.
OH, I THINK YOU DO.

23:11.682 --> 23:13.753
LET ME TELL YOU A LITTLE BIT
ABOUT MY BABY RIGHT THERE.

23:13.786 --> 23:16.592
60 DAYS TO HARVEST,
10 DAYS TO CURE, HYDRO.

23:16.626 --> 23:20.466
YOU'RE LOOKING
AT 85 TO 105‐PLUS CURE DAYS

23:20.499 --> 23:21.669
FROM GERMINATION TO HARVEST.

23:21.702 --> 23:23.372
WE CAN EVEN SHORTEN
THAT CYCLE

23:23.405 --> 23:25.209
WITH FORCED FLOWERING
LIGHTING CYCLES,

23:25.242 --> 23:26.846
TYING IT DOWN,
AND SPLITTING IT.

23:26.879 --> 23:29.083
I HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

23:29.117 --> 23:32.991
I'M SAYING FRONT ME SOME MONEY
FOR SPACE AND EQUIPMENT...

23:33.025 --> 23:36.331
AND WE'LL BE SELLING OUR OWN
SHIT INSIDE OF THREE MONTHS.

23:36.364 --> 23:37.768
AND WHAT AM I SUPPOSED TO DO
IN THE MEANTIME?

23:37.801 --> 23:41.909
BETTER GO MAKE NICE WITH HEYLIA.
PRETEND NOTHING'S GOING ON.

23:41.943 --> 23:45.517
NO OFFENSE ‐‐ GET RID
OF THIS FUCKING BAKERY,

23:45.550 --> 23:49.457
TAKE THE CASH,
AND LET US START A BUSINESS.

23:49.490 --> 23:50.760
[ SIGHS ]

23:50.794 --> 23:53.933
IF YOU DO THIS, HEYLIA
WILL NEVER SPEAK TO YOU AGAIN.

23:55.971 --> 23:57.340
FUCK HEYLIA.

23:57.373 --> 23:59.511
I HEARD EVERYTHING
SHE HAD TO SAY.

23:59.545 --> 24:01.114
WHAT YOU WANT TO DO?

24:09.030 --> 24:11.201
I WANT TO HEAR MORE.

24:13.405 --> 24:15.610
[ CHILDREN SQUEALING HAPPILY
IN DISTANCE ]

24:18.115 --> 24:20.252
PEGGY?

24:20.285 --> 24:22.223
PEGGY?

24:22.256 --> 24:24.160
ISABEL,
THIS IS GRAYSON.

24:24.193 --> 24:25.830
CAN YOU HOLD ON
JUST ONE SECOND?

24:27.901 --> 24:29.203
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

24:29.237 --> 24:32.209
I'M DOING WHAT WE PRACTICED,
AND I THINK IT'S WORKING.

24:32.243 --> 24:33.579
HE REALLY LIKES ME.

24:35.049 --> 24:37.186
YOU LOOK REALLY HOT.
I DO?

24:37.219 --> 24:39.023
YEAH,
YOU'RE REALLY SWEATY.

24:42.496 --> 24:44.467
[ Jewish accent ]
SHALOM, NANCY.

24:44.500 --> 24:46.271
ARE YOU HAVING
A PARTY WITHOUT ME?

24:46.304 --> 24:48.609
[ CHUCKLES ]

24:48.643 --> 24:51.882
I DON'T EVEN WANT TO KNOW.
JUST...GO.

24:51.916 --> 24:54.588
[ Normal voice ]
BUT I AM NOT GOING ANYWHERE.

24:54.621 --> 24:58.028
IN THE MISHNAH AND THE U.S.
MILITARY CODE, IT IS WRITTEN,

24:58.061 --> 25:01.602
"FULL‐TIME STUDENTS
WORKING TOWARD BECOMING
ORDAINED MINISTERS

25:01.635 --> 25:02.904
IN A RECOGNIZED RELIGION

25:02.938 --> 25:04.908
ARE DEFERRED
FROM MILITARY SERVICE."

25:04.942 --> 25:08.081
IN OTHER WORDS, ONCE YOU GO
RABBI, YOU NEVER GO BYE‐BYE.

25:08.115 --> 25:10.052
MAZEL TOV, ANDY.

25:12.189 --> 25:16.464
SO, UH, WHAT'S GOING ON?
YOU CAN CONFIDE IN ME NOW.

25:16.498 --> 25:19.237
I'M SWITCHING AROUND SOME THINGS
WITH THE BUSINESS.

25:19.270 --> 25:20.272
YOU GONNA LET ME PLAY?

25:26.284 --> 25:28.556
Shh!

25:31.261 --> 25:34.802
UNDER STRICT SUPERVISION.

25:34.835 --> 25:36.037
MM‐HMM.

25:46.157 --> 25:50.232
OKAY.
UM...DISTRIBUTION...

25:50.265 --> 25:53.405
MEET FINANCE.

25:53.438 --> 25:55.910
SALES...

25:55.944 --> 25:57.614
LEGAL...

25:58.783 --> 26:00.787
YENTL.

26:05.195 --> 26:07.366
SO, WE GONNA OPEN THE WINE
OR JUST WATCH IT AGE?

26:07.399 --> 26:08.435
CORKSCREW?

26:08.468 --> 26:09.805
OH, JUST A MINUTE.

26:09.838 --> 26:12.476
SO, WHO'S GONNA BE
OUR MUSCLE?

26:12.511 --> 26:15.416
I WOULD DO IT,
BUT I'VE GOT BURSITIS.

26:15.449 --> 26:19.323
DON'T LOOK AT ME.
I WENT TO LAW SCHOOL.

26:22.329 --> 26:23.331
FINE,
I'LL BE THE MUSCLE.

26:24.735 --> 26:27.373
BACK OFF, MAN.
I'M PITCHING TOMORROW.

26:27.406 --> 26:29.343
YOU GO, GIRL.

26:31.481 --> 26:32.951
HI, SWEETIE.

26:32.984 --> 26:34.353
WHAT'S GOING ON?

26:34.387 --> 26:36.424
WHAT?
OH, NOTHING.

26:36.458 --> 26:38.028
I HEARD
YOU AND SILAS FIGHTING.

26:38.061 --> 26:42.303
OH, WE WERE ANGRY,
BUT WE'LL BE OKAY.

26:45.175 --> 26:46.979
ARE YOU SURE?

26:47.012 --> 26:48.516
OF COURSE, HONEY.

26:48.549 --> 26:50.587
WHAT'S GOING ON OUTSIDE?

26:53.559 --> 26:57.767
I WAS LONELY, SO I INVITED
SOME FRIENDS OVER.

27:00.540 --> 27:03.779
SHANE, LOOK AT ME.

27:03.813 --> 27:07.186
EVERYTHING'S
GONNA BE OKAY, ALL RIGHT?

27:08.990 --> 27:10.392
I LOVE YOU.

27:10.425 --> 27:13.733
YEAH, ME TOO.

27:44.293 --> 27:48.235
WHO'S LITTLE BOY ARE YOU?
ARE YOU GRANDMA'S LITTLE BOY?

27:48.268 --> 27:49.838
ARE YOU GRANDMA'S BABY?

27:49.872 --> 27:51.809
YES, YOU ARE.
[ LAUGHS ]

27:51.842 --> 27:53.713
OKAY,
MAYBE YOU WERE READY.

27:53.746 --> 27:55.048
I FUCKIN' TOLD YOU.

27:55.082 --> 27:57.286
